Introduction:

  genhtml parses the LaTeX sources of the draft, and generates a HTML version.

Prerequisites:

  Various Hackage packages.

Usage:

  In this directory, run:

    runhaskell genhtml.hs

  This generates 14882/ with lots of .html files in it.

